<% text_for :title do %>
  The estate is shared equally between the half-brothers or half-sisters.
<% end %>

<% govspeak_for :body do %>
  <% if calculator.region == "england-and-wales"%>
    If a half-brother or half-sister died before the deceased, their children (half-nieces and half-nephews of the deceased) will inherit in their place.

    If any of these half-nieces or half-nephews died before the deceased, their children will inherit in their place.

    If any half-brothers, half-sisters or their descendants died after the deceased, their share will become part of their own estate.
  <% else %>
    If a half-brother or half-sister has died before the deceased died, their children (nieces and nephews of the deceased) inherit in their place.
  <% end %>
<% end %>

